centurio
Class STListStatesTranslator

java.lang.Object
  centurio.STTranslator
      centurio.STListStatesTranslator

public class STListStatesTranslator
extends STTranslator

This class implements the translation from KIF to Prolog, adding a state denoter as additional parameter to each predicate, prefixing (most) names by "ggp_" and variables (except state denoter) by "VAR_". It is from the DTH GGP project.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Holger Troelenberg, David Boehme, Kristine Jetzke, Felix Maximilian Möller, Marius Schneider, Martin Wegner
